:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>"</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>פורום אחיות אחראיות</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>" אחת לחודש  .</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>"</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>פורום סגני אחיות אחראיות</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>" מפגש אחת לרבעון (השתתפות בישיבות אחיות אחראיות ) .</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>"</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>פורום מדריכים קליניים</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>" אחת  לרבעון .</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>"</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>פורום צוות משרד אחות ראשית</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/></a:rPr><a:t>" פגישה אחת לרבעון לקידום תוכניות עבודה.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="he-IL" sz="5000" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="002060"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="David" panose="020E0502060401010101" pitchFamily="34" charset="-79"/><a:cs typeface="David" panose="020E05020604010